import {Card, Col, FloatingLabel, Form, ListGroup, Row} from "react-bootstrap";

function CountryBox(){
    return(
        <Row className="justify-content-center">
            <Col xs={5}>
                <Card className="p-3 shadow-sm navbar-nav-scroll">
                    <Row>
                        <Col>

                            <FloatingLabel
                                label="Country"
                                className="mb-4 text-secondary"
                            >
                                <Form.Control
                                    label="Cuntry"
                                    placeholder="Cuntry"
                                    aria-label="Cuntry"
                                    className="border-3 border-primary"
                                />

                            </FloatingLabel>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                    <Row>
                        <Col>
                            <Card className="modal-dialog-scrollable overflow-auto" style={{maxHeight: 300}}>
                                <ListGroup variant="flush">
                                    <ListGroup.Item action className="text-primary">Cras justo
                                        odio</ListGroup.Item>
                                </ListGroup>
                            </Card>

                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                </Card>
            </Col>
        </Row>
    );
}

export default CountryBox;
